metadata.name: VLW Gratitude #1/4
metadata.description:
This image is a token of my appreciation to my 1/1 Collectors.

The image is typical of my style of images, it’s the beach, it’s the sunshine, it’s the sunset and some wispy stunning clouds.

It’s just my way of saying thank-you for believing in my passion.

So from me, thank-you so very much.

Vicki
